##
## traceopts requestor
##
@node main "Trace options requestor help"

 The TRACE Requestor allows you to specify which trace options you wish
 to include in the compiled file.

 If you enable the trace option and then enable ALL, During execution, the
 trace output is sent to the console, If your program has been started
 from the workbench, a window will Open allowing you to see the trace
 output.

 You can clear any previous setup that you may have had using the Clear
 button at the bottom, ( Keyboard shortcut is DELETE )

 You can Cancel the requestor, reverting back to the previous settings
 by clicking on the Cancel button at the bottom ( Keyboard shortcut is the
 ESCAPE key )

 To use the settings you have chosen, Click on the OK button at the bottom
 ( Or use the Keyboard shortcut key which is `O' )

@endnode
